=== Overview

codec2 is used to support Codec 2.0 for Video/Audio

==== Options

--- true
this option is used to enable support for codec2.0

    --- parameters

    --- code dir
	- frameworks/av/media/codec2
	- frameworks/av/media/bufferpool
	- hardware/interfaces/media/c2/1.0
    - hardware/interfaces/media/bufferpool/2.0

--- false
this option is used to disable support for codec2.0

    --- parameters

    --- code dir

--- default
when not explicitly selected in mixin spec file, the default option will be used.
